parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure to repair or replace defective airbags can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident. Delayed or unavailable repairs can leave vehicle owners at risk.
symptoms: None
as this issue is related to the recall process rather than a specific vehicle malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of airbags to deploy in the event of an accident can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: Airbags fail to deploy in an accident
resulting in injury or death.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Misleading or inadequate repair of airbag issues can lead to a false sense of security, putting vehicle owners at risk.
symptoms: Vehicle owners are led to believe that airbag issues have been resolved
but the problem persists.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, slip gears, or fail to shift, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Delayed gear engagement
slipping or jerking gears
failure to shift
loss of power
and unusual noises.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition interlock system can cause the vehicle to roll away or move unexpectedly, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Key can be removed from ignition without shifting transmission to park
vehicle rolls away or moves unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the key to be removed from the ignition while the vehicle is in gear, leading to unintended movement and potential accidents.
symptoms: The key can be removed from the ignition while the vehicle is in gear
the vehicle can roll away without warning
the ignition key can be removed without the transmission being in park.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to shut off while driving, leading to potential accidents and loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle shuts off while driving
the instrument panel lights fail to illuminate
the alarm system malfunctions
the vehicle will not start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the instrument panel lighting can cause the driver to be unable to see important information, leading to potential accidents.
symptoms: The instrument panel lights fail to illuminate
the lights are dim or flickering
the lights turn off while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the security system can cause the alarm to go off unnecessarily, leading to inconvenience and potential safety risks.
symptoms: The alarm goes off unnecessarily
the car locks itself
the car will not start due to security system malfunction.
